  Unityblog 2.4-stable (~git)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Minimal no fuzz blog, with a neat minimal design

Features:
    comments, tagging, admin add/edit/delete, categories etc.


HOWTO
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

see Screenshots in screenshot/ if you just want a preview...

To Install blog, run as root:
   mysql -u root -p
   create database unityblog
   grant all permissions on unityblog.* to 'unityblog'@'localhost' identified by 'yourpass';
   flush privileges;
   exit

   mysql -uroot -p --default-character-set=utf8 unityblog < scripts/allunity.sql


---------------------------
Admin default user/pw
---------------------------
admin/admin for logging into the blog as admin in top of page, you must change this manually in sql for now!

the admin menu is hidden on top of page, move your mouse up to top center of page of the blog
then log in as admin/admin
